{"tid":1980783,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"才參與Lady Gaga慈善音樂會 Sam Smith自爆感染武漢肺炎","createTime":"2020-04-20T09:41:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-20T09:52:59.000Z","uid":14918,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7aebf154b6a948b5b9b2ce5bc0841eec3049cd46","tid":1980783,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T09:41:59.000Z","msg":"由女神卡卡（Lady Gaga）負責籌畫的WHO《同一個世界：共同在家》群星慈善募款音樂會，近日才剛圓滿落幕，沒想到卻傳出當天參與歌手山姆史密斯（Sam Smith）感染武漢肺炎，時間點甚至是在英國大爆發前，消息一出震驚全球。<br />\n<br />\n英國當紅男歌手山姆史密斯日前接受媒體訪問時，透露自己疑似感染了武漢肺炎，事實上，他並沒有去醫院檢測，「但根據我所瞭解的症狀，我絕對是中了」，他更進一步表示，這些症狀在英國疫情爆發前就出現，且不到一個星期，他的姊姊也出現同樣的感染症狀。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=728926&amp;From=Search&amp;Key=%E5%8D%A1%E5%8D%A1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D728926%26From%3DSearch%26Key%3D%25E5%258D%25A1%25E5%258D%25A1&d=Sy1M3c%2BVV8kZ1V6TqBoGPgomF%2BlBZ%2FxAFwVMru4Rc7Q%3D&h=0f43648b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D728926%26From%3DSearch%26Key%3D%25E5%258D%25A1%25E5%258D%25A1&h=24168112\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=728926&amp;From=Search&amp;Key=%E5%8D%A1%E5%8D%A1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1e69271b2cc6c4276b08d2873f4e4c7482171ef","tid":1980783,"uid":349872,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T09:52:59.000Z","msg":"信世衞，唔怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}